In the Matter of T.D.P. No. 310A04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2005. John Campbell, for Cumberland Co. DSS. Stuart A. Brock, Winston-Salem, Robin Weaver-Hurmence, for Guardian Ad Litem.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th day of March 2005 by Respondent to Strike:

"Motion Dismissed as Moot by order of the Court in conference this the 4th day of May 2005."
